KTTV 18.0 5. Roseanne KABC 16.7 6. Grace Under Fire KABC 15.5 7. 60 Minutes 
KCBS 15.4 8. Married ... With Children KTTV 14.8 9. Seinfeld KNBC 14.5 10. Full 
