</P>
<P>
 5. Morrison & Foerster, San Francisco 
</P>
<P>
 6. Pacific Gas & Electric, San Francisco 
</P>
<P>
 7. Patagonia, Ventura 
</P>
<P>
 8. Silicon Graphics, Mountain View 
</P>
