<P>
 LAPD shake-up -- In some Tuesday editions of The Times, a photo caption 
misidentified a participant in a Los Angeles Police Department news conference 
about a department shake-up. The man identified as Assistant Chief Bernard C. 
Parks was in fact Chief of Staff Ronald Banks. 
</P>
