<TEXT>
<P>
 Todd Fielding -- Statistics and a story in Tuesday's Times Orange County were 
not in agreement with regard to the number of points Mission Viejo's Todd 
Fielding scored in a football game against Santa Ana Valley last Friday. 
Fielding scored 35 points on four touchdowns, two field goals and five extra 
points. 
</P>
