<P>
 Political partners -- In Tuesday's paper, the final paragraph of a story about 
James Carville and Mary Matalin was garbled because of a production error. The 
story should have ended with Carville's comment, "When this era of our life is 
over and we're flat on our backs, we'll or stand on a street corner with a sign 
that says, 'Will bicker for food.' " 
